name: The Cuphead Show!
overview: Follow the misadventures of the impulsive Cuphead and his cautious but persuadable brother Mugman in this animated series based on the hit video game.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Pirate adventures, giant peppermints, devilish pitchforks and more! Wherever Cuphead and Mugman go this season, fun and mischief are sure to follow.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: From hijinks and heebie-jeebies to holiday cheer: This season's got it all as the boys go big to trick the Devil â€” and stir up trouble all over town!

episodes.name: Carn-Evil
episodes.overview: Cuphead convinces Mugman they should ditch their chores and head to the carnival, unaware it's a front to collect souls.

episodes.name: Baby Bottle
episodes.overview: The brothers take care of a baby left at their front door. But with Elder Kettle gone and a strict warning to be good, it's harder than they imagined.

episodes.name: Ribby & Croaks
episodes.overview: A squabbling Mugman and Cuphead sneak into a club to grab some ice cream after the boxing champs who own it steal their money.

episodes.name: Handle with Care
episodes.overview: After Mugman's handle breaks off, the brothers visit a greedy shopkeeper and get creative while on the hunt for glue.

episodes.name: Roll the Dice
episodes.overview: All bets are off when Cuphead takes over Inkwell Isle's No. 1 game show, much to the annoyance of its devious host King Dice and his devilish boss.

episodes.name: Ghosts Ain't Real
episodes.overview: A spooky bunch of ghosts treat Cuphead and Mugman to a night of chills and thrills after trapping them inside a creepy graveyard.

episodes.name: Root Packed
episodes.overview: Cuphead and Mugman have to defend Elder Kettle's precious vegetable garden after a rotten gang turns their yard into a party.

episodes.name: Sweater Off Dead
episodes.overview: Mugman knits a special sweater to keep Cuphead's soul safe. Meanwhile, in the underworld, the Devil is throwing a party.

episodes.name: Sweater Luck Next Time
episodes.overview: The Devil follows the brothers day after day, waiting for Cuphead to take off his sweater so he can collect his soul before Stickler finds out.

episodes.name: Dangerous Mugman
episodes.overview: Cuphead and a cowardly Mugman test their courage after Porkrind sends them on a dangerous errand that quickly gets out of hand.

episodes.name: Dirt Nap
episodes.overview: Elder Kettle overhears strange conversations between Cuphead and Mugman, then worries that the boys have menacing plans for him.

episodes.name: In Charm's Way
episodes.overview: Trouble follows the brothers when Cuphead and Mugman get in over their heads upon meeting a free-spirited, street-smart new friend.

episodes.name: Jail-Broken
episodes.overview: Cuphead and Mugman are in the slammer after breaking into the cookie factory. Prison's scary â€” but now they can't decide whether to bust out or stay in!

episodes.name: Charmed and Dangerous
episodes.overview: Trouble comes a-knockin' when Ms. Chalice turns up on Elder Kettle's doorstep and turns on the charm. The question is: Can she be trusted?

episodes.name: A High Seas Adventure!
episodes.overview: The boys think they're just "playing" pirate until they actually drift out to sea and get roped into a mission to reunite a captain and his sweetheart.

episodes.name: Another Brother
episodes.overview: After an argument with Mugman, Cuphead goes looking for another brother. But his reckless new sibling isn't all he's cracked up to be.

episodes.name: Sweet Temptation
episodes.overview: Cuphead's self-control is put to the test when he discovers a sugary dreamland where he can eat all the sweets he wants... with a catch.

episodes.name: The I Scream Man
episodes.overview: All Mugman wants is a little peace and quiet while Cuphead and Elder Kettle are away. Enter the ice cream man â€” and his jaunty truck's maddening jingle.

episodes.name: Piano Lesson
episodes.overview: Mugman gets dangerously jealous when his snooty piano teacher taps Cuphead to compete for a $10,000 musical prize instead of him.

episodes.name: Release the Demons!
episodes.overview: Steaming mad and ready for revenge, the Devil summons his finest demons and sends them above ground on a mission to recapture Cuphead's soul.

episodes.name: Dead Broke
episodes.overview: Ms. Chalice and the boys craft a perfect spooky scam: making money as ghost removers! But things get real when they pick a house that's already haunted.

episodes.name: Rats All Folks!
episodes.overview: A crafty rat claims ownership of Elder Kettle's cottage and all of its contents after a careless Cuphead and Mugman leave the door open.

episodes.name: Say Cheese!
episodes.overview: Elder Kettle wants to snap a family portrait of him and his boys â€” and, boy, does he get it! Just not in the picture-perfect setting he was expecting.

episodes.name: Lost in the Woods
episodes.overview: Winter's coming and there's lots of work to do, but Cuphead doesn't want to do any of it. Forget chopping wood â€” he'd rather launch rockets into the sky!

episodes.name: The Devil's Pitchfork
episodes.overview: Cuphead and Mugman are giddy with power when they get their hands on the Devil's pitchfork and make fiery mischief all over town.

2.overview: Pirate adventures, giant peppermints, devilish pitchforks and more! Wherever Cuphead and Mugman go this season, fun and mischief are sure to follow.

episodes.name: The Devil's Revenge!
episodes.overview: Without Mugman, Cuphead doesn't know what to do with himself. Can he strike a deal with the Devil to save his beloved brother and bring him home?

episodes.name: Don't Answer the Door
episodes.overview: Knock, knock! Danger's at the door when Elder Kettle goes out to get his mustache waxed, leaving a bumbling Cuphead and Mugman home alone.

episodes.name: Cupstaged
episodes.overview: Sally Stageplay's holding auditions for an exciting new space opera. But Cuphead, Mugman and the Devil all want the same role: the lead.

episodes.name: Roadkill
episodes.overview: After hitting the Devil with his car, Elder Kettle takes him in, mistaking him for a humble house cat he affectionately calls "Mrs. Meow Meow."

episodes.name: Holiday Tree-dition
episodes.overview: With Christmas fast approaching, Elder Kettle sends the boys on an important errand: to pick out the perfect tree.

episodes.name: A Very Devil Christmas
episodes.overview: Christmas brings out the worst in the Devil, who's notoriously naughty... until he schemes to get himself onto Santa's nice list.

episodes.name: Special Delivery
episodes.overview: After breaking Porkrind's window, Cuphead, Mugman and Ms. Chalice must work off the debt by delivering a mysterious package to Ribby and Croaks.

episodes.name: Down and Out
episodes.overview: King Dice â€” the Devil's onetime No. 1 â€” is out of the spotlight. But Cuphead of all people wants to be his manager and help him make a comeback.

episodes.name: JoyRide
episodes.overview: It's time for a day of fun with Elder Kettle... or is it? With an assist from Ms. Chalice, Cuphead and Mugman are scaring up shenanigans all over town!

episodes.name: Dance with Danger
episodes.overview: A fateful flashback reveals what Ms. Chalice's life was like before she met Cuphead and Mugman.
